<p rend="chapter">6-7. Oghayogagocchakaṃ</p>

<p rend="title">32-43. Oghādidukāni</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="1"><hi rend="paranum">1</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Oghaṃ <pb ed="T" n="3.0347" /><pb ed="V" n="3.0365" /> dhammaṃ paṭicca ogho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…pe….</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="2"><hi rend="paranum">2</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Yogaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca yogo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…pe… (dvepi gocchakā āsavagocchakasadisā ninnānākaraṇā).</p>

<p rend="centre">Oghayogagocchakaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.</p>
